column2: SELECT TOP #    mqc.NAME, mqc.RA,   mqc.DEC, mqc.RMAG,   mqc.BMAG, mqc.REDSHIFT,   mqc.TYPE,   distance(   POINT(&&&, mqc.RA, mqc.DEC),   POINT(&&&, dr1#.ra, dr1#.dec)) AS dist FROM mydb.milliquas AS mqc, dbo.PhotoObjAll AS dr1# into mydb.mqcXdr1#_#arcsec WHERE #=CONTAINS(   POINT(&&&, mqc.RA, mqc.DEC),   CIRCLE(&&&, dr1#.ra, dr1#.dec, #) )
